### Destroy [DELETE /api/admin/admin_users/{admin_user_uuid}]
Delete Admin User per given email OR uuid. If both given, UUID takes precedence.

Example

```bash
curl -X DELETE https://railsskeleton.daliaresearch.com/api/admin/admin_users/91fb9777-daa9-4b4e-94c9-1673b941875c \
     -H 'Authorization: Dalia FAKE_ADMIN_TOKEN'
```

+ Parameters
  + `admin_user_uuid`: `91fb9777-daa9-4b4e-94c9-1673b941875c` (string, optional) UUID of Admin User

+ Response 204

+ Response 422 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
  + Attributes (ResponseErrors)
